node.text:
0 to 800k+ in 2 years… top tips on how I did it ⬇️

🔥 Showed my face every once in a while to build a personal connection, put a face behind the name, and build trust

🔥 Provided a mix of educational, inspirational, and entertaining content that always added value

🔥 Put my own spin on viral/trending content to increase relatability

🔥 Engaged with my community by collaborating with others

🔥 Found hashtags that expand my reach and target my ideal audience

🔥 Tried out different types of content and see what performs best (and stick to it)

🔥 Niche down and stick to it

🔥 Check my analytics and recreate top performing posts

The last 2 years, I’ve learned SO much and this is only the tip of the iceberg. 

Sis, if you're ready to take action and claim success TODAY, get on the waitlist before we close the doors for the Ultimate Instagram Blueprint. 

1st link in my bio!! uplevel your account and grow organically at rapid speed.

💋 xo Paula

@womanceomindset 👈🏼

In the past 2 years, I invested thousands of dollars in myself. Courses, mentors, ebooks—girlllll, you name it. 

I did it all and now I’m sharing with you EVERYTHING I learned.
